{"tid":884641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"起登文化已經比連登搞到變哂質","createTime":"2018-10-31T18:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T19:00:01.000Z","uid":156666,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36222f9ebbc4d5dc38f7ab7cd3de3f2cbcda88e4","tid":884641,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"之前要對方係個大仆街 有哂正當理由先會真係去起底<br />\n<br />\n但而家係街見到條女上鏡啲 又冇得罪你地啲咩都要比你地起底 動機完全只係為滿足一已私慾<br />\n<br />\n仲要好多人覺得係冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc265d1c960023052222192b215b5dc8f4529119","tid":884641,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"有無聽過硬膠廠長"},{"pid":"fc85535ab1e6e7ee701f7de65e6be9a48b477a0c","tid":884641,"uid":14144,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:52:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得無得咁講<br />\n最主要原因係因為social media嘅UI變化<br />\n容易左起底 所以依家連登咪成日起到人底<br />\n好似ig咁 以往就算有兩個ac 都唔會有icon係右下<br />\nFacebook留言更加唔會有你個icon係格離<br />\n <br />\n只係因為起底方法多左加容易左 先變到咁樣姐<br />\n<br />\n就算高登時代 都一樣有人無做錯俾人起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1548c2778d34a0fa5ee79bfc3778fec46351e0c2","tid":884641,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T19:00:01.000Z","msg":"新會然"}]}